        { "id": "t3", "type": "content", "variant": "default", "props": { "content": "<h2>Terms of Service</h2><p>Last updated: May 2026</p><h3> Acceptance of Terms</h3><p>By using OpenServe, you agree to these terms.</p><h3>Use of Services</h3><p>You agree to use our services lawful and in accordance with these terms.</p><h3>Accounts</h3><p>You are responsible for maintaining the security of your account.</p><h3>Intellectual Property</h3><p>Our services and content are protected by copyright and other intellectual property laws.</p><h3>Limitation of Liability</h3><p>Our services are provided 'as is' without warranties of any kind.</p>" }},
